   Supplied by their industry and scavenged technologies. There is no shortage of surplus weaponry for the [color=tan]Dynasty[/color] to throw their weight around with. Generally using low-tech and untrustworthy ballistic weaponry for their personnel. Automatic rifles, high caliber side-arms, and explosive personalities.

  [color=green]Strengths:[/color]
  - Equipped with a situational armory, the [color=tan]PDV[/color] can out-prepare for nearly any battle. There is no shortage of variety for this military. This also implies that their is no perfect solution to combat. Everything has a flaw.
  - Having a semi-dated arsenal means there is no direct counter like EMP to combat styles among the [color=tan]Vanguard[/color]. You either overpower or out-skill them in firepower.

  [color=red]Weaknesses:[/color]
  - Being situational means you may often find yourself stuck between a rock and a very powerful foe. Having back-up strategies in the event that you cant defeat them outright is key to success.
  - You will not find many weapon options that are good all-rounders. The [color=tan]PDV[/color] specialize in using what they have to their advantage. Loadouts are what you make out of the [color=tan]Vanguard[/color]'s current supplies.

